{"type":null,"faqId":48050,"title":"共享移动网络","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 1.18125in 0.7875in 1.18125in 0.7875in;}\n.s1{font-weight:bold;}\n.s2{display: inline-block; text-indent: 0; min-width: 0.41527778in;}\n.p1{margin-left:1.18125in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n.p2{margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n.p3{text-indent:-0.110416666in;margin-left:1.18125in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n.p4{margin-bottom:0.027777778in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:9pt;}\n.p5{margin-left:1.4409722in;margin-top:0.027777778in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:9pt;}\n.p6{margin-left:1.18125in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">通过便携式 WLAN 热点共享移动网络</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>通过将手机设置为 WLAN 热点，可以与其他设备共享移动网络。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>XE \"通过便携式 WLAN 热点共享移动网络\"XE \"开启 WLAN 热点\"XE \"设置 WLAN 热点\"</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s2\">1.  </span><span>在主屏幕，点击“</span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=178020\" style=\"width:0.25555557in;height:0.18680556in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span>”“设置”，然后切换到“全部设置”页签。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s2\">2.  </span><span>在“无线和网络”区域，点击“更多”。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s2\">3.  </span><span>点击“移动热点 &gt; 便携式 WLAN 热点”或“移动网络共享 &gt; 便携式 WLAN 热点”。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s2\">4.  </span><span>点击热点开关，开启热点。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s2\">5.  </span><span>点击“配置 WLAN 热点”。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s2\">6.  </span><span>设置 WLAN 热点名称、安全性以及访问密码，然后点击“保存”。</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p4\">\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=178021\" style=\"width:0.5in;height:0.16597222in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n<p class=\"p5\">\n<span>为了保护您的网络安全，建议将安全性设置为 WPA2 PSK。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">通过 USB 共享移动网络</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>通过 USB 数据线，可以将手机的移动网络共享给电脑。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>XE \"通过 USB 共享移动网络\"XE \"开启 USB 共享网络\"XE \"给电脑共享网络\"</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>由于操作系统的差异，在使用此功能前，可能需要在电脑中安装手机驱动程序或建立相应的网络连接。</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p6\">\n<span>1.使用 USB 数据线将手机与电脑连接。</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p6\">\n<span>2.在主屏幕，点击“</span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=178022\" style=\"width:0.25555557in;height:0.18680556in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span>”“设置”，然后切换到“全部设置”页签。</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p6\">\n<span>3.在“无线和网络”区域，点击“更多”。</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p6\">\n<span>4.点击“移动热点”或“移动网络共享”。</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p6\">\n<span>5.点击 “USB 共享网络”开关，共享移动网络。</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p4\">\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=178023\" style=\"width:0.5in;height:0.16597222in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n<p class=\"p5\">\n<span>通过 USB 共享移动网络时，手机将不能作为 USB 存储设备使用。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">通过蓝牙共享移动网络</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>XE \"通过蓝牙共享移动网络\"XE \"开启蓝牙共享网络\"</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>通过蓝牙功能，可以将手机的移动网络共享给其他设备。</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p6\">\n<span>1.在主屏幕，点击“</span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=178024\" style=\"width:0.25555557in;height:0.18680556in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span>”“设置”，然后切换到“全部设置”页签。</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p6\">\n<span>2.在“无线和网络”区域，点击“更多”。</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p6\">\n<span>3.点击“移动热点”或“移动网络共享”。</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p6\">\n<span>4.点击“蓝牙共享网络”开关，共享移动网络。</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":138,"faqType":"网络与数据共享","useful":3,"unUseful":3,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"3636","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-Network-Data-sharing","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1445598102000,"seriesProductName":"RIO-AL00,RIO-CL00,RIO-TL00,RIO-UL00,RIO-UL10","visitedTimes":81,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":null,"avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}